Citation.sTitle: Surface Tension of Binary Mixtures of Ethanol + Ethylene glycol from 20 to 50 oC
Citation.sAbstract: Surface tension data of binary mixtures of ethanol and ethyleneglycol was measured over the entire concentration range at temperatures of 20-50 C. The experimental values were correlated with temperature and with mole fraction. The values of the excess surface tension for these mixtures were also calculated.
